{
    "summary": "List __VAR:entity_plural__",
    "description": "Retrieves a paginated list of __VAR:entity_plural__ with support for filtering, sorting, and relation loading.\n\n## Query Methods\n\n| Method | Use Case |\n|--------|----------|\n| **GET** | Simple queries with pagination only |\n| **PUT** | Advanced queries with filters, relations, and sorting |\n\n## Query Parameters\n\n### Pagination\nControl the result set size and page navigation.\n```json\n{\"pagination\": {\"page\": 1, \"pagesize\": 15}}\n```\n\n### Relations\nEager load related entities to avoid N+1 queries.\n```json\n{\"relations\": [\"user\", \"category\"]}\n```\n- Use `[\"all\"]` to load all available relations\n- Use dot notation for nested relations: `\"user.roles\"`\n\n### Filtering (attr)\nFilter by exact field values.\n```json\n{\"attr\": {\"status\": \"active\", \"type\": [\"A\", \"B\"]}}\n```\n- Multiple values for same field = OR condition\n- Different fields = AND condition\n\n### Advanced Filtering (oper)\nBuild complex queries with operators.\n```json\n{\"oper\": [{\"and\": [{\"0\": \"like|name|%search%|0\"}]}]}\n```\nFormat: `\"operator|field|value|case_sensitive\"`\n\nOperators: `=`, `!=`, `<`, `>`, `<=`, `>=`, `like`\n\n### Sorting\nSort by one or more fields.\n```json\n{\"orderby\": [{\"created_at\": \"desc\"}, {\"name\": \"asc\"}]}\n```\n\n### Field Selection\nReturn only specific fields.\n```json\n{\"select\": [\"id\", \"name\", \"status\"]}\n```",
    "tags": [
        "__VAR:module__"
    ],
    "requestBody": {
        "required": false,
        "description": "Query configuration for filtering, pagination, and relation loading.",
        "content": {
            "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                        "relations": {
                            "type": "array",
                            "description": "Relations to eager load",
                            "items": {"type": "string"},
                            "example": "__JSON:relations_list__"
                        },
                        "pagination": {
                            "type": "object",
                            "description": "Pagination settings",
                            "properties": {
                                "page": {
                                    "type": "integer",
                                    "minimum": 1,
                                    "default": 1,
                                    "example": 1
                                },
                                "pagesize": {
                                    "type": "integer",
                                    "minimum": 1,
                                    "maximum": 100,
                                    "default": 15,
                                    "example": 15
                                }
                            }
                        },
                        "select": {
                            "type": "array",
                            "description": "Fields to return (empty = all)",
                            "items": {"type": "string"},
                            "example": ["id", "name", "created_at"]
                        },
                        "attr": {
                            "type": "object",
                            "description": "Exact match filters",
                            "additionalProperties": true,
                            "example": "__JSON:attr_examples__"
                        },
                        "oper": {
                            "type": "array",
                            "description": "Advanced operator filters",
                            "items": {"type": "object"},
                            "example": "__JSON:oper_examples__"
                        },
                        "orderby": {
                            "type": "array",
                            "description": "Sort configuration",
                            "items": {"type": "object"},
                            "example": "__JSON:orderby_examples__"
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    },
    "responses": {
        "200": {
            "description": "Paginated list of __VAR:entity_plural__ retrieved successfully.",
            "content": {
                "application/json": {
                    "schema": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "properties": {
                            "data": {
                                "type": "array",
                                "description": "Array of __VAR:entity_singular__ objects",
                                "items": "__JSON:model_schema__"
                            },
                            "meta": {
                                "type": "object",
                                "description": "Pagination metadata",
                                "properties": {
                                    "current_page": {"type": "integer", "example": 1},
                                    "from": {"type": "integer", "example": 1},
                                    "to": {"type": "integer", "example": 15},
                                    "per_page": {"type": "integer", "example": 15},
                                    "total": {"type": "integer", "example": 100},
                                    "last_page": {"type": "integer", "example": 7}
                                }
                            },
                            "links": {
                                "type": "object",
                                "description": "Pagination navigation links",
                                "properties": {
                                    "first": {"type": "string", "format": "uri"},
                                    "last": {"type": "string", "format": "uri"},
                                    "prev": {"type": "string", "format": "uri", "nullable": true},
                                    "next": {"type": "string", "format": "uri", "nullable": true}
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "400": {
            "description": "Invalid query parameters provided.",
            "content": {
                "application/json": {
                    "schema": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "properties": {
                            "message": {"type": "string", "example": "Invalid query parameters."}
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "401": {
            "description": "Authentication required.",
            "content": {
                "application/json": {
                    "schema": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "properties": {
                            "message": {"type": "string", "example": "Unauthenticated."}
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "403": {
            "description": "Permission denied.",
            "content": {
                "application/json": {
                    "schema": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "properties": {
                            "message": {"type": "string", "example": "This action is unauthorized."}
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        "500": {
            "description": "Internal server error.",
            "content": {
                "application/json": {
                    "schema": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "properties": {
                            "message": {"type": "string", "example": "Server error occurred."}
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}
